title: Bitcoin Price Ready to Resume Gains: Can the Uptrend Return?
body: Bitcoin price started a fresh increase above the $62,000 zone. BTC is gaining pace and might aim for more gains above the $63,500 zone. A close above the $65,000 resistance might initiate more gains. In the stated case, the price could rise and test the $65,500 resistance level. Any more gains might send the price toward the $66,500 resistance level. Are Dips Supported In BTC? If Bitcoin fails to rise above the $64,000 resistance zone, it could start another decline.
